a. Set Home/Respawn Point<br>
b. You can bind yourself anywhere. Other targets can only be bound within a town zone. (with the exception of Timerous Deep, which is a no bind zone)<br>
c. can be purchased in enchanter, cleric, shaman, wizard, necro, druid, and caster guilds.<br>
<br>
Charm<br>
a. single target<br>
This spell charms the target and turns it into a pet of the caster. <br>
b. level limit 25<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Choke<br>
a. single target DoT<br>
Direct Damage (18 - 20)<br>
Decrease Strength (7 - 10)<br>
Decrease Agility (7 - 10)<br>
Damage over Time (60 hitpoints over 30 secs) <br>
b. It will stack with all spells in game with the exception of Heart Flutter and Asystole series.<br>
c. lasts 30 seconds<br>
d. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Ebbing Strength<br>
a. single target debuff<br>
Decrease Strength (21 - 25)<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Enduring Breath<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Unlimited Breath Underwater<br>
b. requires fish scales<br>
c. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Cabilis, Grobb, Halas, Oggok Shaman Guilds<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
Kelethin, Rivervale, Surefall Druid Guilds<br>
Kelethin Ranger Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: Dark Elf<br>
a. self only illusion and buff<br>
Change Form (Dark Elf)<br>
Faction Modifier (Dark Elf) <br>
ultravision<br>
b. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: Erudite<br>
a. self only illusion<br>
Change Form (Erudite)<br>
Faction Modifier (Erudite)<br>
bad night vision<br>
b. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: Halfling<br>
a. self only illusion<br>
Change Form (Halfling)<br>
Faction Modifier (Halfling)<br>
b. can be purchased in Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: High Elf<br>
a. self only illusion and buff<br>
Change Form (High Elf)<br>
Faction Modifier (High Elf)<br>
improved night vision<br>
b. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Kilan`s Animation<br>
a. summon pet<br>
b. requires 1 tiny dagger<br>
c. can be purchased in Highhold Keep<br>
<br>
Languid Pace<br>
a. single target debuff<br>
Decrease Attack Rate (18% - 30%)<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Memory Blur<br>
a. Single Target Hate List Reduction<br>
b. It can also be used to terminate NPC pets that have lost their masters. (this does not work on all npc pets)<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Mist<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase AC (6 - <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
