c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Serpent Sight<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Infravision<br>
b. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
Gypsies<br>
<br>
Thicken Mana<br>
a. Single Object Enchantment<br>
Create: Vial of Viscous Mana<br>
b. requires a pearl and a poison vial<br>
c. can be purchases in Brownie Camp in Lesser Fay<br>
